Greenko Profit Almost Triples as Acquisitions Boost Energy Assets

-- B y   D o u g l a s   L y t l e
-- 
2011-09-19T06:05:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/greenko-profit-almost-triples-as-acquisitions-boost-energy-assets.html
Greenko Group Plc (GKO) , a U.K. 
developer of clean-power projects in  India , said pretax
earnings rose 188 percent as new acquisitions and concessions 
added to its energy portfolio.  Pretax profit climbed to 14 million euros ($19.2 million) 
in the year ended March 31, the Douglas, Isle of Man-based 
company said today in a regulatory statement. Greenko is on 
schedule to reach a targeted 1 gigawatt of operational 
capacity in 2015, it said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Douglas Lytle at 
 dlytle@bloomberg.net  